      <li>Turn left onto SP68 and follow signs to Cecina</li>
      <li>Merge onto SP39 toward Rosignano Marittimo</li>
      <li>Continue south on Via del Littorale to Quercianella</li>
      <li>Arrive at Villa Tara, Via don Italo Gambini 11</li>
    </ol>

